OL,3,C'I was very lucky' - Man airlifted to
OL,4,Chospital following bicycle crash
OL,6,FA man who suffered serious injuries
OL,7,Fafter he had an accident on his
OL,8,Fbicycle in Dumfries and Galloway has
OL,9,Fpraised the air ambulance charity that
OL,10,Fhelped him.
OL,12,FPeter Rogerson fell from his bike in
OL,13,FEskdalemuir in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,14,Fhalfway through a 45 mile cycle.
OL,16,FThe 66-year-old from Lochmaben spoke
OL,17,Fabout what happened when he was sent
OL,18,Fflying off of his bike.
