OL,3,C'I was very lucky' - Man airlifted to
OL,4,Chospital following bicycle crash
OL,6,FHe said: "I normally do 45 miles and
OL,7,Fit takes me about three hours. I was
OL,8,Fhalfway into my ride and was going
OL,9,Fdownhill and as I went round a corner
OL,10,Fmy bike toppled over and I came off.
OL,12,F"I was very lucky. I was cycling on a
OL,13,Fquiet road, and while normally that
OL,14,Fwould be great for a cyclist, you
OL,15,Fnever think about what if you need
OL,16,Fpeople to come and help you."
OL,18,FThe Great North Air Ambulance Service
OL,19,Fwere requested to attend and flew from
OL,20,Fthe base in Langwathby near Penrith.
