OL,3,C'I was very lucky' - Man airlifted to
OL,4,Chospital following bicycle crash
OL,6,FPeter Rogerson's wife Alison and his
OL,7,Ftwo daughters are now raising money
OL,8,Ffor the GNAAS by running a number of
OL,9,Fhalf marathons.
OL,11,FAlison said: "The amazing team were
OL,12,Ffirst on scene following the 999 call
OL,13,Ffrom the people that found him. Their
OL,14,Fquick treatment and care ultimately
OL,15,Fincreased his chance of survival."
OL,17,FPeter Rogerson had suffered a broken
OL,18,Fcollarbone, 10 broken ribs, multiple
OL,19,Ffractures including a flail chest, a
OL,20,Ffractured pelvis and a broken finger.
