OL,3,C'I was very lucky' - Man airlifted to
OL,4,Chospital following bicycle crash
OL,6,FMrs Rogerson added: "Peter had injured
OL,7,Fhis left side, but his head was fine
OL,8,Fand there was no injury to it. His
OL,9,Fhelmet was split in two and ultimately
OL,10,Fsaved his skull and brain."
OL,12,FPeter was flown to the Queen Elizabeth
OL,13,FHospital in Glasgow where he underwent
OL,14,Fan eight hour operation to fit metal
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,FPeter had no recollection of what
OL,18,Fhappened following the accident and
OL,19,Fthought he had completed his bike ride
OL,20,Fwhen he woke in hospital.
