OL,3,C'I was very lucky' - Man airlifted to
OL,4,Chospital following bicycle crash
OL,6,FMr Rogerson was in hospital from 11
OL,7,FDecember 2023 until 27 December where
OL,8,Fhe has been using a walking stick and
OL,9,Fis undergoing physiotherapy to aid
OL,10,Fwith his recovery.
OL,12,FHe said: "I've had falls on my bike
OL,13,Fbefore and usually dust myself down
OL,14,Fand go home. I've broken my collarbone
OL,15,Fon the other side, but nothing like
OL,16,Fthis before.
OL,18,F"I still say to my wife, I can't get
OL,19,Fmy head round what happened. I just
OL,20,Fthink, wow these people kept me alive."
